headline: Baird Q4 2024 Mid Cap Growth Strategy Commentary
summary: For the quarter, the Baird Mid Cap Growth portfolio produced a negative return of -1.3%, net of fees, trailing the Russell Midcap Growth increase of +8.1%.

headline: Datadog: Still Has Bite Left In It
summary: Datadog is a 'boring' technology business that used to be a widely hyped stock, but then became underloved. Read why I think now is the best time ever to buy the DDOG stock.
